text:
Riverside Park: Three views in a southwestward direction across the Hudson River from a point near General U.S. Grants' Tomb (West 122nd Street). Lying amid stream is the U.S. Fleet on display and silhouetted against the Jersey highland.

May 10, 1915.

Walter L. Bogert.
title: Manhattan: Riverside Park - 122nd Street (West).
